@startuml
actor Student
participant Frontend
participant Backend
participant "AI Service" as AI
database Database

Student -> Frontend: Start scenario
Frontend -> Backend: POST /sessions
Backend -> Database: Save session
Backend --> Frontend: Session with initial stakeholder message

Student -> Frontend: Ask question
Frontend -> Backend: POST /sessions/{id}/messages
Backend -> AI: Generate stakeholder response
AI --> Backend: Response and revealed requirement ids
Backend -> Database: Save messages
Backend --> Frontend: Updated conversation

Student -> Frontend: Submit requirements
Frontend -> Backend: POST /sessions/{id}/submissions
Backend -> AI: Evaluate against rubric
AI --> Backend: Scores and feedback
Backend -> Database: Save evaluation
Backend --> Frontend: Feedback result
@enduml
